---
// Services component - Modern business services
---

<section class="services" id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">Our Expertise</span>
      <h2>Services We Provide</h2>
      <p>Comprehensive web development and digital solutions tailored to your business needs</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="ri-globe-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Web Development</h3>
        <p>
          Custom-built websites and applications using modern technologies. 
          Fully responsive, fast-loading, and optimized for conversions.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Responsive Design</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Performance Optimized</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> SEO Ready</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="ri-design-2-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>
        <p>
          Beautiful, intuitive interfaces that users love. Strategic design that 
          drives engagement and converts visitors into customers.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> User Research</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Wireframing</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Visual Design</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="ri-smartphone-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>App Development</h3>
        <p>
          Powerful mobile and web applications built with cutting-edge frameworks. 
          Scalable solutions that grow with your business.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Frontend & Backend</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Database Design</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> API Integration</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="ri-search-2-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>SEO & Performance</h3>
        <p>
          Get found online with proven SEO strategies. Lightning-fast performance 
          that improves rankings and user experience.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> On-page Optimization</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Speed Optimization</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Analytics Setup</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="ri-mail-send-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>E-commerce Solutions</h3>
        <p>
          Complete online store solutions with secure payments and inventory management. 
          Turn your ideas into revenue.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Shopping Cart</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Payment Integration</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Order Management</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <i class="ri-settings-3-line"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Maintenance & Support</h3>
        <p>
          Ongoing support and maintenance to keep your website secure and running smoothly. 
          Latest updates and improvements.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> 24/7 Monitoring</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Security Updates</li>
          <li><i class="ri-check-line"></i> Technical Support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    color: #3b82f6;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #64748b;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: #3b82f6;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .service-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .service-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .service-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .service-list i {
    color: #3b82f6;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .services-grid {
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
